title: The Lady is a C***
description:
Written by Kristen Bartlett
Featuring: Keith Kingbay, Audrey Stanfield, Lauren Brickman, Ryan Farrell, Kate Sidley, Bardia Salimi, and Alex Estrada

Performed at The Upright Citizen's Brigade Theater as part of Maude Night (5/11/15).
Directed by: Ellena Chmielewski.
Shot by: Jocelyn Roueiheb
